        <h3>1692 - Salem, Massachusetts</h3>
        <p>Some scholars of the occult have theorized that the entity known as Liveda may have played a role in the Salem Witch Trials...</p>

        <h3>1348 - Florence, Italy</h3>
        <p>During the height of the Black Death, there were scattered reports of a grinning figure seen walking among the dead...</p>

